title: Arsenal targeting Gokhan Tore transfer, say reports
text: Arsenal targeting Gokhan Tore transfer, say reports Sunday, 4 October 2015 (3 minutes ago) Arsenal have set their sights on a move for Besiktas winger Gokhan Tore, according to reports. Tore’s Besiktas side are currently top of the Turkish SuperLig, with the 23-year-old winger hitting three goals in his first eight appearances this season.
